		"description": {
			"value": "<p>Wondrous Item - Uncommon</p><p><em>This pinch of sparkling dust collapses light around everything nearby.</em></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Action</strong> - 10 ft Emanation (Self)</p><p>Take a Utilize action to cast the dust into the air. You and every creature or object within 10 feet of you gain the Invisible condition for [[/r 2d4]] minutes. The dust is consumed.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Properties</strong></p><ul><li><p>The duration is shared by every affected target.</p></li><li><p>The Invisible condition ends on a target immediately after it makes an attack roll, deals damage, or casts a spell.</p></li></ul>",
